AuraDescription_lang: $?a313413[|CFFFFd200- Mask of the Burned Bridge|RWhen moving, spawn void zones behind you that drain Sanity.][]$?a313414[|CFFFFd200- Mask of the Daredevil|RIncreases Sanity damage from creatures by $s3%.][]$?a313415[|CFFFFd200- Mask of the Dark Imagination|RWhile below $s4% of maximum Sanity, occasionally summon enemies from the Void.][]$?a313416[|CFFFFd200- Mask of the Long Night|RReduces maximum Sanity by $s5%.][]$?a313417[|CFFFFd200- Mask of the Pained|RRenders the wearer prone to additional simultaneous Madnesses.][]$?a1216878[|CFFFFd200- Mask of Multitudes|RMore enemies will be present in the vision.][]$?a1223175[|CFFFFd200- Mask of the Nemesis|RA nemesis of yours will spawn after a number of kills within the Horrific vision.][]$?a1224539[|CFFFFd200- Mask of Vengeance|RKilling enemies will bolster their nearby allies damage by $w8%.][]Increases Corrupted Mementos gained.Enemy damage increased by ${$w1*$w6}%.Enemy health increased by ${$w2*$w7}%.
